                      float yRot,

                      float xVel,
                      float yVel,
                      float zVel)
        Add an object to this simulation and adjust its translation to fill the screen.
        Parameters:
        object - : Object to be modeled in the simulation
        xRot - : Angular Position about x axis
        yRot - : Angular Position about y axis
        zRot - : Angular Position about z axis
        xVel - : Angular Velocity about x axis
        yVel - : Angular Velocity about y axis
        zVel - : Angular Velocity about z axis
